00:43:14,926 --> 00:43:16,092
- Mom.

544
00:43:16,094 --> 00:43:17,627
- Please don't
      argue with me okay?

545
00:43:17,629 --> 00:43:19,963
- I don't wanna get in trouble.

546
00:43:19,965 --> 00:43:20,930
Just call 'em.

547
00:43:22,133 --> 00:43:24,100
- All right, I'll call.

548
00:43:27,706 --> 00:43:29,906
